articles.title: CS favours tech-driven measures, real-time coordination to curb cyber frauds
articles.description: 36th UTLCC Excelsior Correspondent JAMMU, Jan 27: Chief Secretary, Atal Dulloo today emphasised the need for robust technology-driven solutions, strengthened enforcement mechanisms and real-time coordination among regulators and law enforcement agencies to effectively curb cyber frauds and online financial scams.
